snippet.textDisplay: Wow...I've listened to this album over and over since I got it and this song Falling I keep coming back to. It will not leave my thoughts through the day. Absolutely beautiful lyrics and music. Harry delivers a flawless performance here and shows a bit of his vulnerability. The sound, the look, the bittersweet melody and lyrics. Wow...a show stopper. I loved Harry in 1D back then and I love Harry Styles now and his two amazing albums. True genius writing his own lyrics to his songs on Fine Line makes it more personable in my opinion. Harry appeals to a broad audience. There is something for everyone. He truly is a shining star.
